{"tid":1296304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"竊美晶片技術給中國，台裔教授恐面臨 219 年刑期","createTime":"2019-07-08T10:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T05:57:05.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e841433691c9c3bb2e941f1b737f2c685bb5d24","tid":1296304,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:28:33.000Z","msg":"竊美晶片技術給中國，台裔教授恐面臨 219 年刑期<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/07/08/professor-stealing-chip-technology-sentence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F07%2F08%2Fprofessor-stealing-chip-technology-sentence%2F&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=e0032773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/07/08/professor-stealing-chip-technology-sentence/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國加州大學洛杉磯分校（UCLA）台裔兼任教授石宇琦企圖替中國竊取應用在軍方的美國晶片技術，遭控 18 項聯邦罪名確定，恐面臨高達 219 年刑期。<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n《新聞週刊》（Newsweek）報導，64 歲的石宇琦被控涉及密謀從一家美國公司違法取得晶片，並將它們出口至中國。這些晶片可能會被用在飛彈、戰機等廣泛的軍事系統。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部 2 日宣布，石宇琦面臨法定刑期最高達 219 年。<span style=\"color: red;\">去年 12 月，本案共同被告、加州巴沙迪納（Pasadena）居民梅傑安（Kiet Anh Mai，譯音）已對參與這項陰謀的走私罪名認罪，預計今年 9 月 19 日宣判，屆時可能面臨法定刑期最高達 10 年。</span><br />\n<br />\n石宇琦佯裝顧客，向一家未具名的美企購買單晶微波積體電路（MMIC）晶片。<br />\n<br />\n司法部在新聞稿說，這些晶片接著被運給名為成都嘉石科技的中企，石怡池曾在該公司擔任總裁。成都嘉石科技當時正在發展自己的 MMIC 晶片工廠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">MMIC 晶片可應用於飛彈、雷達、電子戰等廣泛的商務與軍事用途，被視為敏感技術，未獲美國商務部批准授權不得出口，而石宇琦沒有這項授權。<br />\n<br />\n這家受害公司是美國空軍、海軍與國防先進研究計畫局（DARPA）等機構的供應商。</span><br />\n<br />\n新聞稿也解釋，經過 6 週審訊後，法院認定石宇琦犯下密謀違反國際緊急經濟權力法（IEEPA）、郵電詐欺、電匯詐欺、虛報納稅額、對政府機構做虛假陳述與策劃犯下網路偷竊，目前未確定宣判日期。"},{"pid":"bf85b03bf9cdba59ce9f0f817d982a11dfe37cee","tid":1296304,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9fedc748ba11434eb5bf5e32fafb295b637a26","tid":1296304,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"偷到都整唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c68db88d516bfdf4e1cb26aa186829737c6e25","tid":1296304,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"219年"},{"pid":"1ee0a0823b2bbf17cff3bd8d05d95d64694427ef","tid":1296304,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f652dd2a7b3b440e889797cb35acf4e91c9a78","tid":1296304,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}